20:45.780 --> 20:47.290
Sayang, pendapat awak pula?

20:54.780 --> 20:55.720
Jurulatih Lu,

20:56.390 --> 20:57.740
Haochen kini telah direkodkan

20:57.740 --> 20:59.650
