26:35.260 --> 26:37.120
Lin, saya akan cari awak lagi lain kali.

26:37.390 --> 26:38.330
-Baik.
-Saya pergi dulu.

26:39.020 --> 26:40.300
-Jumpa Jumaat nanti.
-Baik.

26:40.300 --> 26:41.240
Selamat tinggal.

26:41.390 --> 26:42.330
Hati-hati.

26:47.910 --> 26:48.850
Zheng.

26:49.100 --> 26:50.200
Bagaimana? Awak tak apa-apa?

26:50.390 --> 26:51.300
Kaki saya terseliuh.

26:51.300 --> 26:52.250
Boleh bergerak lagi tak?

26:52.430 --> 26:54.040
Sakit, tak boleh bergerak.

26:54.990 --> 26:56.090
Kalau begitu, mari kita pergi hospital.

26:56.540 --> 26:57.580
Jangan berlengah.

26:57.580 --> 26:58.870
-Mari.
-Mari.

26:58.870 --> 26:59.810
Pengurus.

27:02.580 --> 27:03.500
